# Installation

To install for all users, run terminal as administrator and execute:

```powershell
cd C:\Users\Public\Documents
git clone --recurse-submodules git@github.com:holmescharles/dwagoon.git
pip install .\dwagoon
```

Then add the following to your PowerShell profile (run `notepad $PROFILE` to open it):

```powershell
Import-Module "C:\Users\Public\Documents\dwagoon\dwagoon.psm1"
```

Download wallpapers with `reddit`.

Change wallpapers and themes with `rice`.

Do not install in editable mode -- otherwise other users will not be able to access the files.
